message: “A NC man has been charged in connection with trafficking twin 14-year-old girls from SC. Derrell Davion Russell, 26, of Shelby, met the two teens, who thought he was close to their age, on social media and got them to agree to meet up with him.” https://buff.ly/2YRLaPd
